Clacy Watson HERRERA, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 12-1461. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 7, 2013. Case below, 704 F.3d 480 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit denied. Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
